OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThere will be some bright or
OL,6,Fsunny spells on Sunday, although a
OL,7,Fscattering of showers are also likely,
OL,8,Fone or two of which could be heavy
OL,9,Fwith some hail and thunder. The strong
OL,10,Fand gusty southwesterly wind will
OL,11,Fslowly ease.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers near southern and
OL,14,Fwestern coasts overnight, but becoming
OL,15,Fdry inland with clear spells. Turning
OL,16,Fchilly with a rural frost. The odd fog
OL,17,Fpatch forming in the lighter winds too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
