OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FMonday should start mostly
OL,6,Ffine with some sunshine. However,
OL,7,Fshowers will break out during the day,
OL,8,Fturning locally heavy and thundery.
OL,9,FFeeling less chilly than recently with
OL,10,Fgentle winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,13,FTuesday should begin bright, although
OL,14,Fit will turn cloudy and breezy with
OL,15,Fpatchy rain developing. Wet and windy
OL,16,Fweather on Wednesday, then sunshine
OL,17,Fand showers on Thursday. Temperatures
OL,18,Frising slightly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
